%% Diagram: API Decision Tree
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart TB
    need{What do you need?} -->|Source string → buffer| render["render()"]
    need -->|File → buffer| renderFile["renderFile()"]
    need -->|File → disk| renderToDisk["renderDiagramFileToDisk()"]
    need -->|Directory → disk| renderAll["renderAll()"]
    need -->|Live re-render| watch["watchDiagrams()"]
    need -->|Isolated pool| runtime["createRendererRuntime()"]
